The '''Greater Javin''' was a region of [[Realspace|space]] in the [[Outer Rim Territories]] of [[the galaxy]].<ref name="TFABG" /> It consisted of the [[Javin sector]]<ref name="BMF" /> and its two subsectors, the [[Anoat sector|Anoat]] and [[Yarith sector|Yarith]] [[sector]]s.<ref name="Art of Uprising" />

